{"article_id":"DVpsA7GUWy0OuZh5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trump Picks CNBC Commentator Larry Kudlow As Top Economic Adviser","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump has picked economist and CNBC commentator Larry Kudlow as director of the White House National Economic Council ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"and Kudlow has accepted the post ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"the White House said Wednesday .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Kudlow , 70 , will replace Gary Cohn ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"who stepped down","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"after losing a battle","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"against imposing tariffs on steel and aluminum imports .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"`` Larry Kudlow was offered , and accepted , the position of Assistant to the President for Economic Policy and Director of the National Economic Council , ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Sanders said .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"`` We will work to have an orderly transition","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"and will keep everyone posted on the timing","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"of him officially assuming the role . ''","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"A longtime free-markets conservative","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"who worked on Wall Street ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Kudlow supports most traditional Republican fiscal policies ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"which may quiet concerns among congressional Republicans and investors","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that the president will surround himself with trade protectionists .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Kudlow has known Trump for years","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"and advised him on policy matters during the 2016 campaign .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"He largely supports the president 's agenda","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and has been a big advocate of his tax cuts .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"`` Trump and the GOP are on the side of the growth angels with the passage of powerful tax-cut legislation","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"to boost business investment , wages , and take-home family pay , ''","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Kudlow wrote","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"after the Republican tax bill passed in December .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"But he has criticized Trump 's trade policies .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"For example , he recently said","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"any move","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"to withdraw from the North American Free Trade Agreement","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"would be a `` calamitously bad decision . ''","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Like Cohn , he also opposed the steel and aluminum tariffs","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"announced earlier this month ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"telling CNBC :","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` In the Reagan years , we used to call the free traders the 'white hats ' and the protectionists the 'black hats . ' The black hats won this time around","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"and I 'm very sorry ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"because it will damage the economy to some extent . ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"Kudlow told The Wall Street Journal","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"he had voiced his concerns to the president","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and was encouraged by Trump 's decision","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"to exempt Canada , Mexico and Australia from the tariffs .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"`` He said to me several times ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"' I believe in global trade .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"I regard myself as a global trader ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"but it has to be fair trade","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"to protect America , ' ``","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Kudlow told the Journal .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"`` I 'm on board with that .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"I personally hope","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"widespread tariff use - it does n't come to that .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"But in some cases , it will . ''","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"On his recent podcast , Kudlow noted :","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"`` Mr. Trump has a negotiating style","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"that is very interesting to me .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"He comes at you -","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"like he 's going to punch you in the teeth with all these tariffs .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"But then he pulls back","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"and starts making ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"you know ,","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"negotiating deals","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"that can work .","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"That looks to me like ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"you know ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"that 's his art of the deal .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"It 's in his book .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"That looks to me like what he 's doing here on tariffs .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"He comes out really hard and strong .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Scares everybody .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"But then he starts to pull back","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"and withdraw . ''","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Kudlow does not have an economics degree .","depth":3},{"id":71,"text":"After serving in the White House Office of Management and Budget under President Ronald Reagan ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"he was hired as chief economist at Bear Stearns .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"But he was forced out amid struggles with drug use , a problem","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"he has spoken about publicly .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Since then he has been a regular commentator and host on CNBC","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"and has written often on economic matters .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"But he was criticized for repeatedly downplaying the economy 's troubles in the months","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"leading up to the Great Recession .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"`` There ai n't no recession , ''","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"he wrote in December 2007 .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"`` The Bush boom is alive and well . ''","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"Kudlow also warned","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"that subsequent Federal Reserve policies","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"aimed at stimulating the economy","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"would lead to higher inflation ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"which did n't happen .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":173,"left":0,"right":172,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":155,"right":171,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":122,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":98,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":93,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":89,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":88,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":4,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":5,"right":90,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":94,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":10,"right":95,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":102,"right":120,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":99,"right":101,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":15,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":103,"right":119,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":